name: Fomo Eth
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
FOMO is a culture, an atmosphere

What makes your project unique?
We are more like a cultural token, people always stand together because of cultural identity, so we are

History of your project.
I am very happy, this is our first project, although the market seems to be not very good now, but we will make the project better
What’s next for your project?


What can your token be used for?
As a carrier of culture at present, more applications will be launched in the future
